    "Management": {
      "text": "Discontinue eye makeup and contacts use until resolved\nWarm compresses\nAntibiotics\nConsider oral antibiotics (with\nstaph\ncoverage) if patient has concurrent\nperiorbital cellulitis\n(rare)\nLittle evidence that topical antibiotics are helpful",
      "subsections": {},
